reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely fit/good buy
reviews.reviewText: I bought this product to upgrade my Powder room. I must say it added a very nice touch and some must needed storage. This product is pretty solid, easy to assemble and the compact design is awesome for small spaces.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute water resistant shelf for my bathroom
reviews.reviewText: Although the shelf is not super sturdy looking, it meets my needs for a small corner unit in the bathroom on which to put extra toilet paper, etc. It was easy to put together and, yes it is plastic, but that is what I wanted because my bathroom is high humidity.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Assembly required - but easy
reviews.reviewText: The item comes in 8 pieces plus 10 screws and a screwdriver. It took about 10 minutes to put together solo, as the parts slip out of alignment when you add a piece, but would be much easier with a second pair of hands.Material is like a laminated plastic over foam core. We’ll use this near our shower, so time will tell whether the humidity will penetrate the softer edges.For now, it’s stable, substantial enough to hold bathroom essentials on a small scale, and attractive. Makes good use of otherwise wasted space. A Black Friday value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Looks Cute - but thats it.
reviews.reviewText: Using a coupon on top of an already marked down price, i paid $16 for this. And for that price id say yes, this is worth buying. Its small, the shelves can hold about the sude of a roll of toilet paper. Its very light which makes it wobbly -ish. So i wouldnt put a candle on it for fear of tip over etc and if ihad paid the original $34 price id send it back immediately. But if youjust need like a tp holder etc its not bad. Cute design. Good price.
